==English==

===Etymology===
A form of [[w:Winston Churchill|Winston Churchill]]'s quotation, made in a radio broadcast in October 1939:
* "I cannot forecast to you the action of [[w:Soviet Union|Russia]]. It is a riddle, wrapped in a mystery, inside an enigma; but perhaps there is a key. That key is Russian national interest."

